    subgraph "Automated Cleanup Lambda"
        H1["Lambda Function: cost-optimizer
        Schedule: Daily at 2am UTC
        Timeout: 15 minutes
        Memory: 512MB"]

        H2["Cleanup Actions:
        1. Identify idle resources (>7 days)
        2. Check tag 'DoNotDelete'
        3. Snapshot EBS volumes
        4. Delete unattached EBS
        5. Delete old snapshots (>90d)
        6. Stop idle EC2 (dev/test only)
        7. Send summary report"]

        H3["Safety Mechanisms:
        - Dry-run mode (default)
        - Whitelist by tag
        - Production exclusion
        - Rollback capability (snapshots)"]

        H4["Cost Impact Example:
        Resources cleaned per month:
        - 50 EBS volumes: 50 × 100GB × $0.10 = $500
        - 20 snapshots: 20 × 50GB × $0.05 = $50
        - 10 idle EC2 (t3.medium): 10 × $30 = $300
        Monthly savings: $850
        Lambda cost: $2
        ROI: 42,400%"]

        H1 --> H2 --> H3 --> H4
    end

